<description language="en">&lt;b&gt;MacroFab, INC. EAGLE Design Rules&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
This DRC check is for 4-Layer Standard Capability boards to be manufactured through the MacroFab, INC. service. Use Layer 2 and 15 for inner layers.</description>
